Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five mil...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They messed up my turf and stole five mil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them get away with that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch the man who's responsible for this and bring him to me without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If push comes to shove... go ahead and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been my dream for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to build a mountain of hamburgers in front of me like this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and eat heartily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Cal, about what we were talking about earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Judy's shooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about... how to go about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to avenge Judy for me? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the kind who fire away with machine guns, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... because you don't look strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you can't trust me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to worry. I'm not the one who'll do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask my friend to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.61,0:01:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a friend like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it but I've got lots of contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I know the shooter's looks and clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my friend will find and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me about the shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see your friend avenge Judy with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Reiji, please let me see that friend of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I'll ask your friend. Please take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinary people like you can't set foot in that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No means no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Cal... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask my friend if they're okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll tell you once my meeting with your friend is decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like I can get in touch with people like that right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try contacting my friend tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about it again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we were behind in our rent for months,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got kicked out this morning. Will you let me stay with you tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's it going, Lizzie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the investigation going smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom is checking up on that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm investigating the matter myself, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, give me a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to hear good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who on earth hindered our deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Godo Family is absolutely vital to solidify my position in Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let something like this get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... So this is your place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems kinda... lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more than enough to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't waste the leftover hamburgers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you'll stay here until you finish them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bedroom is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use that bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you use to live with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Just a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did, a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I use your shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll just pretend to be that friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Having you owe me one isn't such a bad deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So does she really seem to know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That doesn't sound very assuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I forgot to grab a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I find it funny that the notorious Mr. Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is taking orders from a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you're letting her stay with you, don't do anything stu-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hung up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:06:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing snooping around in my backyard, Lizzie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. My friend said yes and will contact me tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Reiji... Do you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your parents already...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I ran away from the worst damn excuse of a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Judy took me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't for her, I'd have been dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you two are sisters, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. She's the only family I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Judy is dead now and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Judy's dead, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I go? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know... what to do, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People die in different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who suffer quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also those who are forgotten with no one crying for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least Judy has you crying for her. She's fortunate for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I go? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the witness... in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a dull pad you've got, eh, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed that Lizzie was having some rats snoop around in town
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to dig something up, so I got her to tell me all sorts of interesting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make her spit out everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ordinary girl can't see anything in such a dark place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's lying about having seen the shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to protect that girl even if it ends up in bloodshed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me want to see her even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Claudia are up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 o'clock tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you explain all this in front of McGwire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who the traitor is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:11:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Phantom. I couldn't keep pretending to know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't this a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna convince them tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll somehow make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that girl really doesn't...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she doesn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything... Right, Cal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew I was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who came earlier... That's Isaac Wisemel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Bloodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all called you Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who that is. Judy's friends told me that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he goes around the country killing gangsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real assassin then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom, the assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the money those yakuza people had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I counted it. There's five million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you... steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't steal it! Such dirty money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't use even one cent of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for someone like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who'd help me for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Phantom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please kill them all. You can have this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who came to that alley last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who fired a gun there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who was supposed to receive this money...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please kill every single one who was involved in Judy's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the estimate for my assassination fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll discuss this tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for lying to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation is heading in a bad direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't found the shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the five mil came rolling in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the organization finds out about this money, I can't make any excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please kill every single one who was involved in Judy's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I make both Cal and the organization understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't explain it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we talk alone, Wisemel will be suspicious of us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain everything in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, explain yourself, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Then first, please let me clear up the misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm sheltering the girl who's supposedly a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's just a family member of the passerby who was dragged into this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and doesn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that for sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Phantom. I have skills to deal with that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a stupid excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like that to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:16:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's no evidence, it doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you use a truth serum on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about recorded data?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you're telling us to trust you at your word?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give it up, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. McCunnen. Do you have anything to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have anything else to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my reasons for not using a truth serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that reason serious enough that you pointed a gun at Isaac?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because I didn't want to destroy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! So now you're a humanitarian?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a different potential in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want it to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. She's got a rare quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even call it a talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An intense motivation to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a hellish solitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost who has nowhere to belong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talent... Someone told me a similar thing in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you're saying that you want to train that girl as an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll become skilled enough to become my right hand in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the proof of this talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop screwing with us, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't something that can be explained with words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though it may be hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for someone whose sight is clouded by doubts and fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want a new assistant that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that you have problems with your current pairing with Lizzie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true that we have lots of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me teaming up with Phantom is too unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom is a genius and I'm mediocre.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's someone whom he approves as his partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to take over my position whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding that prostitute, whose name is Judy Devens or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who was killed along with the yakuza...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain that she had nothing to do with this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She's clean. Totally clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it because we investigated thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph... What do you say, Isaac?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to accept it, Ray?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't produce results...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the rest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we shall see how you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an interesting act, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be deceived. Not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you vixen's lap dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. It was my mistake to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that you want to produce more people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it in order to protect that girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that you've sold her that much, you'll be held accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing has been resolved after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shooter...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five million dollars...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge for Judy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is probably a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it okay to make her take the same path as mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
